targets.queryText:
SELECT 
    datetime,
    AVG(CASE WHEN algorithm_name LIKE 'Dilithium%' THEN duration ELSE NULL END) AS Dilithium,
    AVG(CASE WHEN algorithm_name = 'ECDSA' THEN duration ELSE NULL END) AS ECDSA,
    AVG(CASE WHEN algorithm_name LIKE 'Falcon%' THEN duration ELSE NULL END) AS Falcon,
    AVG(CASE WHEN algorithm_name LIKE 'SPHINCS+%' THEN duration ELSE NULL END) AS Sphincs
FROM crypto_tests_data
WHERE test_name = 'GenerateKey'
GROUP BY datetime
